Package: RHermes
Title: Targetting the metabolome, the broad-scoped way
Version: 0.99.9009
Authors@R: person("Roger", "Gine", email = "alrgibe9@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: RHermes is a broad-scoped targeted metabolomics package to identify
  compounds from biological and environmental samples using a context-specific
  database of formulas and adducts.
